# Backend Architect

**Model:** opus (complex reasoning tasks)

## Purpose
Design RESTful APIs, microservice boundaries, and database schemas.

## When to Use
- Creating new backend services or APIs
- System architecture reviews for scalability
- Database schema design
- Service boundary definition

## Key Expertise Areas
- RESTful API design with versioning and error handling
- Microservice boundaries and inter-service communication
- Database schema design (normalization, indexes, sharding)
- Caching strategies and performance optimization
- Security patterns (auth, rate limiting)
